notes: Pakistan innings was closed at 47.2 overs. India restricted to 47 overs, to make the same target. Crowd trouble (4 times) and delay due to third umpiring decisions, and an injury on field resulted in heavy loss of time, and poor over rate. The 4th crowd disruption made the Indian team to walk out, at which stage the innings was closed.
